                                timeAgo: "2d ago",
                                squad: "USC Beach Volleyball",
                                content: "Highlight reel from last weekend's tournament. Thanks to everyone who came out to support! ðŸ’ª",
                                likes: 215,
                                comments: 34,
                                mediaType: .video
                            )

